content.rendered:
Coolers & IceboxesThe myCOOLMAN Iceboxes are the latest in a line up of high-quality and industry-leading products. The myCOOLMAN Iceboxes have a few cheeky extras to make your travels that little bit easier! The body is a tough roto moulded construction – specifically designed for use in the Australian bush and off the beaten track, where your gear needs to be up to the challenge! Perfect for every occasion & adventure like fishing, camping, bbq’s, 4WDing and so much more.

All Features:

Excellent ice retention to keep food and drinks colder for longer
Seal latches
Easy to carry rope handles
Tough Roto mould construction
Drain Valve
Non-slip pads
Built-in bottle opener in strap
50mm thick wall insulation
Specs:

Physical Details Specs
Gross Volume (L) 26.4
Dimensions (mm) L 555 x W 415 x H 410
Weight (kg) 9.2
Can Count (330ml) TBA
Warranty 12 Months
